{"tid":2337941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年度十大流行語是：新冠肺炎","createTime":"2020-12-23T15:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T18:29:27.000Z","uid":306111,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4898122b1de85dd1e375c42cc09a143abcd4f1ea","tid":2337941,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"12月21日，中國國家語言資源監測與研究中心與商務印書館、人民網等聯合主辦的&ldquo;漢語盤點2020&rdquo;揭曉儀式在北京舉行。最終，&ldquo;民&rdquo;&ldquo;脫貧攻堅&rdquo;&ldquo;疫&rdquo;&ldquo;新冠疫情&rdquo;分別當選年度國內字、國內詞、國際字、國際詞。<br />\n<br />\n2020年度十大新詞語是：復工復產、新冠疫情、無癥狀感染者、方艙醫院、健康碼、數字人民幣、服貿會、雙循環、天問一號、無接觸配送。<br />\n<br />\n2020年度十大流行語是：新冠肺炎、抗疫、復工復產、民法典、網課、雙循環、人類衛生健康共同體、抗美援朝70周年、六穩六保、嫦娥五號。<br />\n<br />\n2020年度十大網絡用語是：逆行者、秋天的第一杯奶茶、帶貨、雲監工、光盤行動、奧利給、好家夥、奪冠、不約而同、集美。<br />\n<br />\n奧利給<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe80a1c3cecd21c66443840f6b164b4e6fe811e","tid":2337941,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"一齊上網課，奧力給，skrskr的"},{"pid":"78d79c5778f6724d5be3b2bf2038abeaab62856e","tid":2337941,"uid":48889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:59:48.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"ee2123a65a1238605e407f646bd8864b69dfaf73","tid":2337941,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e6d985c1fc6d4294c158f9b5568b4d9f8a63e9","tid":2337941,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee2123a65a1238605e407f646bd8864b69dfaf73","tid":2337941,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"你這個好家顆，奧力給 ! 為你點讚一個"},{"pid":"a5c844db21608270aa9fbf9ef7249c5994f33bd9","tid":23